  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "overview",
      "label": "Overview",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "meta",
          "uid": "bdqql4lte"
        },
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Overview",
          "uid": "bqkhsfqvx"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "We were given a rare brief take a product that millions of people use, throw out everything, and start over.\nNew name, new code, new design. No legacy constraints.",
          "uid": "b296xfwk2"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Zapp Account is HDFC Bank's reimagined digital wallet rebuilt from scratch in partnership with Zeta.\nNew name, new identity, new codebase in Flutter, and a fundamentally different model for how users could get access to it. What made this different from a rebrand: the product had a structural limitation that no amount of visual redesign could fix. We had to solve that first.",
          "uid": "bvmm279x1"
        },
        {
          "uid": "badwemv1x",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        }
      ],
      "uid": "bd8owpf9e"
    },
    {
      "id": "problem",
      "label": "Problem",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Problem",
          "uid": "b2agz61e3"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "PayZapp has had a digital wallet for quite some time, but it hasn't effectively attracted new users. Despite having UPI functionality, many users remain unaware of it and aren't engaging with the product as we hoped. To address this, we need to clarify our user acquisition strategy and boost both active usage and new sign-ups. It's essential to define the value proposition we want to communicate to potential users.",
          "uid": "b6z9wlq5p"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "To address this challenge, we should broaden our approach by refining our user acquisition strategy and boosting both active engagement and new registrations. Since this is an HDFC Bank product, it's important to highlight the core value they offer, as they are sponsoring this significant transformation to attract a wider audience.",
          "uid": "b0b1ndgm0"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b52va8nmz",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        }
      ],
      "uid": "bnoyp5h4x"
    },
    {
      "id": "process",
      "label": "Process",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Process",
          "uid": "bj24ey8xl"
        },
        {
          "type": "eyebrow-heading",
          "eyebrow": "",
          "headline": "The Old Scenario",
          "uid": "b5362y6b2"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "text": "The product was functional but never communicated its own value. Users had no clear sense of what it was for, where to use it, or why it was better than what they already had.",
          "media": {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232078:b6kfqytkq",
            "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "b2n56t1hj",
            "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/b2n56t1hj-zapp-account-b2n56t1hj",
              "originalName": "clipboard-1781856232144.png",
              "mimeType": "image/png",
              "size": 356364,
              "resourceType": "image",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232078:b6kfqytkq",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-19T08:03:52.144Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "btkmp89ae",
          "reverse": false
        },
        {
          "uid": "bbtci6msx",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "text": "Introduction of UPI happened. But the adoption was still slow. The UI never changed meaningfully to reflect what was new. And the reason to use the product was not set clear.",
          "media": {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232145:b9y94ch6q",
            "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "bro1bdd73",
            "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/bro1bdd73-zapp-account-bro1bdd73",
              "originalName": "clipboard-1781856232146.png",
              "mimeType": "image/png",
              "size": 371447,
              "resourceType": "image",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232145:b9y94ch6q",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-19T08:03:52.146Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "bz022b03j"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "This set the starting point for the rebrand. Before designing anything new, I needed to understand what the data was actually saying who was using the product, where they were dropping off, and what they were ignoring.",
          "uid": "b7dg0m4rw"
        },
        {
          "uid": "br1qtmnzj",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bmaczgt2y",
          "type": "metrics",
          "style": "standard",
          "items": [
            {
              "uid": "bhk67hbs1",
              "stat": "X%",
              "label": "ABC",
              "note": ""
            },
            {
              "stat": "Z%",
              "label": "ABC",
              "note": "",
              "uid": "bqovvttn4"
            },
            {
              "stat": "Y%",
              "label": "ABC",
              "note": "",
              "uid": "bpspeeoh0"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "uid": "bcw3zuhct",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "The goal wasn't just to ship a new visual language. It was to design a product that could speak to both the users already in the ecosystem and the new ones we needed to acquire and make sure neither group felt like the product wasn't built for them.\nThat meant the first question wasn't a design question. It was: who is this product actually for?",
          "uid": "bs0boyqx4"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b5jjznqjx",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md",
          "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232150:bc8yjynts",
          "mediaMimeType": "image/png"
        },
        {
          "type": "eyebrow-heading",
          "eyebrow": "",
          "headline": "The Proposed Direction",
          "uid": "btoid4r9s",
          "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232150:bc8yjynts",
          "mediaMimeType": "image/png"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "The brief from the bank was clear: <strong>relaunch with a new identity, new name, and a stronger reason for users to come back.</strong> But the real challenge wasn't the rebrand it was adoption. How do you re-introduce a product to people who've already dismissed it, without making them feel like they're being sold something new?",
          "uid": "bkrft9bsl"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Multiple rounds of conversations with the HDFC team helped shape this. The goal wasn't to hide the history of PayZapp it was to build on it. Existing users needed continuity. New users needed a reason to care.",
          "uid": "baz5mu3tk"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<strong>Two things had to be true from the start:</strong>",
          "uid": "b260yyg7b"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bteq547px",
          "type": "image",
          "layout": "2-col",
          "src": "",
          "alt": "",
          "hideCaptions": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781960639879:be21i6quu",
              "alt": "image",
              "uid": "bbwcmexhv",
              "caption": "Give users real value, immediately. Not a promise of features later",
              "mediaType": "image",
              "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
              "cloudinary": {
                "status": "pending-upload",
                "field": "src",
                "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/bbwcmexhv-image",
                "originalName": "image.png",
                "mimeType": "image/png",
                "size": 178353,
                "resourceType": "image",
                "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781960639879:be21i6quu",
                "createdAt": "2026-06-20T13:03:59.887Z"
              }
            },
            {
              "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781960650114:b7g1yobdm",
              "alt": "image",
              "uid": "bkw4g7p6d",
              "caption": "Don't make it feel like a migration. Rather make it an upgrade",
              "mediaType": "image",
              "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
              "cloudinary": {
                "status": "pending-upload",
                "field": "src",
                "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/bkw4g7p6d-image",
                "originalName": "image.png",
                "mimeType": "image/png",
                "size": 170817,
                "resourceType": "image",
                "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781960650114:b7g1yobdm",
                "createdAt": "2026-06-20T13:04:10.128Z"
              }
            }
          ],
          "mediaHeight": 250,
          "spacing": "tight"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b3j59yvh2",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bz2z2vpxr",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        }
      ],
      "uid": "bn4eyhfao"
    },
    {
      "id": "design",
      "label": "Design",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Design",
          "uid": "b6z8big9l"
        },
        {
          "type": "eyebrow-heading",
          "eyebrow": "",
          "headline": "Rounds of iteration",
          "uid": "bu4ho6hgm"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Nothing came easy. The product went through multiple rounds of direction changes across product managers, bank leadership, and internal teams. Information architecture was rethought more than once. What looked right one week got challenged the next.",
          "uid": "bxvjh20jc"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "layout": "wide",
          "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232150:bc8yjynts",
          "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
          "uid": "busact944",
          "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
          "cloudinary": {
            "status": "pending-upload",
            "field": "src",
            "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/busact944-zapp-account-busact944",
            "originalName": "clipboard-1781856232152.png",
            "mimeType": "image/png",
            "size": 649182,
            "resourceType": "image",
            "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856232150:bc8yjynts",
            "createdAt": "2026-06-19T08:03:52.152Z"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Every round made the product sharper. Here's what we landed on.",
          "uid": "b1hleysqv"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bahnnys2i",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "Let’s Onboard you",
          "text": "Getting a new user in someone with no HDFC history required a flow that felt fast and guided. We refined the onboarding to reduce friction at every step, with Video KYC as the centrepiece. The handoff to and from the SDK had to feel seamless.",
          "media": {
            "type": "video",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781979790777:bshl8ycca",
            "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "bsy7x35a2",
            "mediaType": "video",
            "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4",
            "autoplay": true,
            "loop": true,
            "controls": false,
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/onboarding",
              "originalName": "Onboarding.mp4",
              "mimeType": "video/mp4",
              "size": 915765,
              "resourceType": "video",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781979790777:bshl8ycca",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-26T00:38:00.000Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "bzr0iwgvg",
          "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bm8yfteoo",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "Homepage",
          "text": "The home screen is the product's first argument. Balance visible immediately, actions within reach, nothing buried. One screen that tells the user exactly what they have and what they can do.",
          "media": {
            "type": "video",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856244196:bl0lzy1g3",
            "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "b3o4grj75",
            "mediaType": "video",
            "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4",
            "autoplay": true,
            "loop": true,
            "controls": false,
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/zapp-home",
              "originalName": "Zapp Home.mp4",
              "mimeType": "video/mp4",
              "size": 543376,
              "resourceType": "video",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781856244196:bl0lzy1g3",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-26T00:38:00.000Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "bzal1lu8t",
          "reverse": true,
          "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bspacer-wtnu-1",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "Welcome to New Users",
          "text": "For someone opening the app for the very first time, the experience had to feel familiar without being patronising. A short welcome moment that explained what Zapp was, why it mattered, and what they could do next without slowing down the people who already knew the drill.",
          "media": {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1782581351851:biaverbn7",
            "alt": "Welcome flow for new Zapp Account users",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "bmedia-wtnu-1",
            "mediaType": "video",
            "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4",
            "autoplay": true,
            "loop": true,
            "controls": false,
            "localAsset": {
              "status": "local",
              "field": "src",
              "originalName": "Screen Recording Jun 27 2026.mp4",
              "mimeType": "video/mp4",
              "size": 752534,
              "resourceType": "video",
              "ref": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1782581351851:biaverbn7",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-27T17:29:11.867Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "bhorizontal-wtnu-1",
          "reverse": false,
          "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4"
        },
        {
          "uid": "brl4wwppm",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "Balance & Delight",
          "text": "The balance display wasn't just a number it was an interaction moment. A small but deliberate detail that made the product feel alive rather than static. Useful information delivered with a bit of character.",
          "media": {
            "type": "video",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1782612000000:bbalancevd",
            "alt": "Balance interaction on Zapp Account",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "bjhjof4qd",
            "mediaType": "video",
            "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4",
            "autoplay": true,
            "loop": true,
            "controls": false,
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/balance",
              "originalName": "Balance.mp4",
              "mimeType": "video/mp4",
              "size": 172457,
              "resourceType": "video",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1782612000000:bbalancevd",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-26T08:58:00.000Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "b6mc1cbzu",
          "mediaMimeType": "video/mp4",
          "reverse": true
        },
        {
          "uid": "bgguc7mi8",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "Nudges",
          "text": "Each action on the home screen carried a nudge a short contextual cue that told users what it did and why it mattered. Especially important for users coming in fresh, with no prior PayZapp context.",
          "media": {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781857889963:b375vscv0",
            "alt": "Zapp Account hero screens",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "b5591rluy",
            "mediaType": "image",
            "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
            "cloudinary": {
              "status": "pending-upload",
              "field": "src",
              "publicId": "portfolio/zapp-account/b5591rluy-image",
              "originalName": "image.png",
              "mimeType": "image/png",
              "size": 93565,
              "resourceType": "image",
              "localAssetRef": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1781857889963:b375vscv0",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-19T08:31:29.981Z"
            }
          },
          "uid": "ba4l9ingm",
          "reverse": false
        },
        {
          "uid": "bspacer-pzhw-1",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontal",
          "headline": "PayZapp Home Widget",
          "text": "A surface beyond the app itself a home-screen widget that brought balance, quick actions, and recent activity one tap away. It gave Zapp a presence in users' daily flow without forcing them to go indise every time, and reinforced the product's promise of being immediate and within reach.",
          "media": {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "cs-asset:zapp-account:1782581420999:bmqypzunk",
            "alt": "PayZapp home-screen widget concept",
            "device": "wide",
            "uid": "bmedia-pzhw-1",
            "mediaType": "image",
            "mediaMimeType": "image/png",
            "localAsset": {
